      "title": "Northbridge Insurance – Fleet telematics program",
      "body": "Managing a fleet is complex—but your insurance doesn’t have to be. Northbridge Insurance’s telematics-enabled program is designed to help you make informed decisions and improve safety, and unlock potential savings. By sharing telematics data through your existing Electronic Logging Devices (ELDs), you can have access to potential automobile premium discounts and gain actionable insights to improve fleet performance.",
